00:00:14.490 --> 00:00:18.155
so many skills utilized by data scientists in the field.

00:00:18.155 --> 00:00:20.040
You started out by learning about

00:00:20.039 --> 00:00:23.309
the Data Science Process and the broad steps that need to be taken to

00:00:23.309 --> 00:00:25.579
go from a question of interest all the way to

00:00:25.579 --> 00:00:28.369
conveying findings to an audience and deploying results.

00:00:28.370 --> 00:00:32.225
You then learn how to use best practices in software engineering.

00:00:32.225 --> 00:00:35.975
You learned how to write effective code and how to test your code.

00:00:35.975 --> 00:00:37.625
