00:00:54.270 --> 00:00:58.330
Most recently, you developed your skills with two important applications of

00:00:58.329 --> 00:01:02.905
data science techniques: experiment design and recommendation engines.

00:01:02.905 --> 00:01:05.290
Looking at the list of skills covered,

00:01:05.290 --> 00:01:08.720
you should be proud of what you've accomplished up to this point.

00:01:08.719 --> 00:01:12.159
Now, it's time for one final challenge before you

00:01:12.159 --> 00:01:15.319
complete the program, the Capstone Project.

00:01:15.319 --> 00:01:17.844
